  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bcb\u0ba9\u0bbe \u0ba4\u0bca\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1 \u0bae\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bae\u0bcd \u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "One more death due to corona infection was recorded in the country",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Government Information Department has reported that one more death due to corona infection has been reported in the country yesterday.",
        "It is noteworthy that only one woman above 60 years of age has died due to corona infection."
      ],
